snippet.title: Gunnelvision [start to finish]
snippet.description:
I bought the "Blockjam 2016" Bundle back in November, but never bothered to check out what was in it.  The Mojang game is either too odd for me to understand, or isn't a real game, but then I checked out a game called "Gunnelvision" in the bundle, and what a game it is.  The only two songs in the bundle are pretty awesome hardcore metal and I like the song enough that it didn't get old for me.

This is a playthrough from beginning to end, there may be a couple moments where the picture/audio cuts out for a moment (this was because I forgot to lock my cursor to the game monitor with DMT).  Sadly the game had to be completed within a timeframe, so there just wasn't enough time for a full-fledged campaign with more maps.
